	<h1 class="title">把老图书馆改成老少皆宜的空间，来看美国这个示范</h1>
	<div class="author-date clearfix">					
			<div class="author clearfix">
					<span class="avatar x25 circle">
						<img src="/system/users/faces/161922/small/161922.jpg?1442322894" alt="">
					</span>
				<span class="name">廖婷 </span>
			</div>
		<span class="date smart-date" data-originDate="2016-04-27 07:08:19 +0800"></span>
	</div>
	<div class="banner">
			<img src="/system/articles/articleshows/26060/medium/26060.jpeg?1461685071" alt="" />			
	</div>
